{"tid":992138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唱歌飆高音！女歌手台上突倒落全尖叫　「瞬間猝死」畫面曝光","createTime":"2019-01-23T02:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T03:25:37.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a79860f95b9bd949b95a2b5974a317fc93af347b","tid":992138,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3854/3854125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3854%2F3854125.jpg&h=7d7f8fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲俄羅斯女歌手飆高音時，突然從舞台上倒了下來。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n俄羅斯一名女歌手卡盧莉娜（Fenia Khaliullina）舉辦演唱會，演唱一首歌曲飆了高音時，沒想到突然倒臥在舞台上，被發現時已經猝死身亡，享年53歲，嚇壞所有的粉絲。<br />\n綜合外電報導，卡盧莉娜與她的樂團「永恆之星」（Everlasting Stars）正舉行演唱會，透過影片可以看到，她唱歌時中氣十足，音準也非常好，完全沒有走音的情形。沒想到當她飆到一段高音時，突然在舞台上倒了下來，所有歌迷看到都嚇傻了。<br />\n卡盧莉娜被送醫急救，仍被宣告不治身亡。根據報告指出，卡盧莉娜的主要死因是心臟病發。<br />\n2016年，台灣歌王郭金發在高雄演唱《燒肉粽》一曲時，也突然倒下，送醫急救後宣告不治，同樣發生歌手猝死在舞台上的死亡事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-rTdq-s0Gq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-rTdq-s0Gq4&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=a5824e01\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-rTdq-s0Gq4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190123/1363404.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190123%2F1363404.htm&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=8c1eb381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190123/1363404.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cbf5ce652760ab6dd46e9350dd163a7979fb4e19","tid":992138,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d388ff372980d35e69f6b7272e96616f5511b187","tid":992138,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hk